Description:
btowc() function: convert unibyte character to wide character.

Files:
lib/btowc.c
m4/btowc.m4
m4/locale-fr.m4

Depends-on:
wchar
mbtowc          [test $HAVE_BTOWC = 0 || test $REPLACE_BTOWC = 1]

configure.ac:
gl_FUNC_BTOWC
if test $HAVE_BTOWC = 0 || test $REPLACE_BTOWC = 1; then
  AC_LIBOBJ([btowc])
  gl_PREREQ_BTOWC
fi
gl_WCHAR_MODULE_INDICATOR([btowc])

